precis:
Amendment to Order in Council P.C. 1990-2142 which authorized the transfer
to the Province of MANITOBA, of the administration and control of two
parcels of vacant land (4.68 hec) situate near Shamattawa and Brochet,
Manitoba, correcting the description of the land.
